- "Champions of engagement" refers to the top users in terms of time spent on the site.; 
- "Spending over 10 minutes" refers to the total time spent (time_spent) being greater than 600 seconds.; 
- "Showing some activity" means there is at least one entry in the activity logs for the user-site combination.

sql:
SELECT AVG(session_duration) AS average_session_duration
FROM sessions
WHERE session_duration > 1800;
